---
// RelatedLinks.astro
---

<hr style="margin: 3rem 0; border: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);" />

<div class="related-links" style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
  <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--text-main);">関連シミュレーター</h3>
  <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem;">
    <li>
      <a href="/nisa-tsumitate/" style="color: var(--primary); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; padding: 0.5rem; border-radius: 4px; transition: background-color 0.2s;" onmouseover="this.style.backgroundColor='var(--bg-body)'" onmouseout="this.style.backgroundColor='transparent'">
        <span style="font-size: 0.8em;">▶</span> 新NISA積立シミュレーター
      </a>
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="/nisa-withdraw/" style="color: var(--primary); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; padding: 0.5rem; border-radius: 4px; transition: background-color 0.2s;" onmouseover="this.style.backgroundColor='var(--bg-body)'" onmouseout="this.style.backgroundColor='transparent'">
        <span style="font-size: 0.8em;">▶</span> 新NISA取り崩しシミュレーター
      </a>
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="/nisa-tax-compare/" style="color: var(--primary); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; padding: 0.5rem; border-radius: 4px; transition: background-color 0.2s;" onmouseover="this.style.backgroundColor='var(--bg-body)'" onmouseout="this.style.backgroundColor='transparent'">
        <span style="font-size: 0.8em;">▶</span> 新NISAと課税口座の税比較
      </a>
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="/account-compare/" style="color: var(--primary); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 500; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; padding: 0.5rem; border-radius: 4px; transition: background-color 0.2s;" onmouseover="this.style.backgroundColor='var(--bg-body)'" onmouseout="this.style.backgroundColor='transparent'">
        <span style="font-size: 0.8em;">▶</span> おすすめ証券口座診断
      </a>
    </li>
  </ul>
</div>
